TIME TO CARE FOR ROSES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Give attention to roses at this time. Prune them before spraying to reduce the 
total area that needs to be sprayed at this time. Remember to drench the 
branches and trunk until the material runs off the branches. 
</P>
