Westminster Size: 1,900 square feet with four bedrooms, three bathrooms, 
two-car garage, 3,500-square-foot lot. Price: $260,000. Down payment*: 20% from 
sale of previous residence. Loan program*: Conventional. Features*: 7.25% fixed 
rate for 29 years. Mortgage payment*: $1,750 a month. Association dues*: Less 
than $75 a month. Tax benefit*: $450 a month Mortgage payment on current home: 
$725 a month. Tax benefit of current home: $200 a month. Net change from moving 
up*: -$850 a month. * Because the Christiansens have not yet opened escrow or 
