<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWS, TIPS & BARGAINS; CALLING ALL DUDE RANCHERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Would-be dudes in search of the right ranch will want to mosey through "The 
Dude Rancher," a 32-page directory of the 111 members of the Dude Ranchers' 
Assn. 
</P>
<P>
 The ranches, which are spread through 11 states (mostly in the Rocky 
Mountains), generally are open from May or June through the fall. Southwestern 
ranches are open November-May. Weekly rates range from $660 to $1,450 per 
adult, depending on accommodations, meals and program. 
</P>
<P>
 To obtain a copy of the directory, send $5 to the Dude Ranchers' Assn., P.O. 
Box G471, LaPorte, Colo. 80535. For information, call (303) 223-8440. 
</P>
</TEXT>
