 Some schools sustained heavy damage, while others had minimal damage and some 
had none. Officials are still assessing the damage and no dollar estimate is 
available. Parents should call the school site. If no answer, call (213) 
251-3300. 
</P>
<P>
 The following Catholic schools are scheduled to reopen Monday unless otherwise 
noted: 
