 Cal Lutheran's spring semester graduate classes in Woodland Hills and North 
Hollywood will be postponed until Monday, Jan. 31. Other colleges will be open. 
</P>
<P>
 The Ventura campus of Cal State Northridge expects to start the spring 
semester Feb. 7 instead of Jan. 31. 
</P>
<P>
 The following Simi Valley schools were scheduled to reopen Monday, while the 
