 * Young Israel of Beverly Hills synagogue 
</P>
<P>
 8701 Pico Blvd., east of Robertson Boulevard. Call (310) 275-3020. WATER 
</P>
<P>
 Free water is available from 7 a.m. to midnight at the following locations. 
Recipients must bring their own containers. There is no limit; trucks refill 
and return to sites throughout the day. 
